reviews.subject: Introduction to Computer Science
reviews.review: Professor Carter is an excellent teacher! She explains complex concepts clearly and is always willing to help students.

reviews.subject: Linear Algebra
reviews.review: Prof. Lee knows his stuff, but his lectures can be dry at times. Homework assignments were challenging.

reviews.subject: Calculus II
reviews.review: Dr. Kim is amazing! She makes math fun and is incredibly supportive. Highly recommend!

reviews.subject: Physics I
reviews.review: Prof. Brown's lectures were difficult to follow. The exams were extremely tough.

reviews.subject: Chemistry
reviews.review: Dr. Garcia is passionate about chemistry and makes it engaging. Lab experiments were fun.

reviews.subject: Biology
reviews.review: Prof. Johnson is knowledgeable but has a monotone teaching style. Textbook was helpful.

reviews.subject: Psychology
reviews.review: Dr. Taylor is an inspiring professor! Her lectures were thought-provoking and discussions were engaging.

reviews.subject: History
reviews.review: Prof. Wilson's lectures were boring and repetitive. Exams were mostly memorization-based.

reviews.subject: English Literature
reviews.review: Dr. Patel is a great professor! She has a passion for literature and encourages critical thinking.

reviews.subject: Philosophy
reviews.review: Prof. Davis is intelligent but his lectures can be abstract. Class discussions were interesting.

reviews.subject: Sociology
reviews.review: Dr. Rodriguez is an amazing professor! She cares about her students and creates a welcoming classroom environment.

reviews.subject: Economics
reviews.review: Prof. Miller's lectures were dry and hard to follow. Textbook was more helpful than class.

reviews.subject: Political Science
reviews.review: Dr. Hall is knowledgeable and passionate about politics. Class discussions were lively.

reviews.subject: Art History
reviews.review: Prof. Lee knows his stuff but his lectures can be boring. Textbook was visually appealing.

reviews.subject: Music Theory
reviews.review: Dr. Carter is an inspiring professor! She makes music theory fun and accessible to everyone.

reviews.subject: Theatre
reviews.review: Prof. Kim's class was disorganized and lacked structure. Assignments were unclear.

reviews.subject: Dance
reviews.review: Dr. Brown is a passionate and inspiring dance instructor. Class was challenging but rewarding.

reviews.subject: Film Studies
reviews.review: Prof. Garcia is knowledgeable but her lectures can be dry. Movie screenings were interesting.
